</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-41_ pf-text-1"><strong>Higher-risk environments (e.g., factories, construction sites) </strong>- Additional supplies such as burns dressings and eye wash.

</li></ul><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-43_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">It is also recommended that employers conduct regular risk assessments to tailor their first aid provisions to the specific conditions of their site, ensuring compliance and efficacy.
